Added `description` and `description_loaded` fields to `SubtaskInfo`. Created `read_description_file` method that issues a `cat` command for the subtask's `description` file with a `"read-description"` context type. Added the call in the `"ls-subtasks"` handler alongside existing `read_patch_file` and `read_subtask_state` calls. Added a `"read-description"` match arm in `handle_command_result` to store the output. Extracted the loading gate into `all_files_loaded()` (checks both `patch_loaded` and `description_loaded`) and `finish_loading()` helpers, used by both `"read-patch"` and `"read-description"` handlers.